CopperLP Research Code

Version: 0.1.0
Status: Development snapshot
Last updated: 2026-07-23

This repository contains five SageMath research scripts accompanying our work on computing asymptotic bounds for the automated Coppersmith method via linear programming.

The included scripts are:

- CIHNP_CSURF.sage
- MIHNP.sage
- ECHNP.sage
- LCG.sage
- LIPH_POKE.sage

Each script is executed independently. Experimental parameters are configured manually in the configuration section near the beginning of the corresponding script.

The repository is provided as a research code archive. It is not an installable software package and does not provide an automated batch runner.

SageMath 10.8 or later is recommended. The optional msolve backend is disabled by default and is not required for running the scripts.
